#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "Amahinanzira"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:18
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the shortcut key arrangements used by &sheets; select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts... </"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will launch a dialog box as shown below."
msgstr ""
"Guhindura... i Iy'ibusamo Urufunguzo Byakoreshejwe ku &kspread; Guhitamo "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu> </guimenu> <guimenuitem> ... </guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> . A Ikiganiro Agasanduku Nka munsi . "

#. Tag: phrase
#: config.docbook:27
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut config screenshot 1"
msgstr "1 "

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:30
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search through the list box to find the action you want to add or change the "
"shortcut keys for and select it by <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking "
"on the name. By entering the name of the action in the search bar at the top "
"you can quickly find the desired action. You will then be able to change the "
"shortcut by selecting the <guilabel>None</guilabel>, <guilabel>Default</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Custom</guilabel> radio button."
msgstr ""
"Gihinguranya i Urutonde Agasanduku Kuri Gushaka i Igikorwa Kuri &Ongera "
"Cyangwa Guhindura... i Iy'ibusamo Utubuto ya:  na Guhitamo ku <mousebutton> "
"Ibumoso: </mousebutton> ku i Izina: . i Izina: Bya i Igikorwa in i Shakisha "
"Umurongo Ku i Hejuru: Gushaka i Igikorwa . Hanyuma Kuri Guhindura... i "
"Iy'ibusamo ku i <guilabel> </guilabel> , <guilabel> </guilabel> Cyangwa "
"<guilabel> Kunozaidosiyeya </guilabel> Akabuto Cyangwa ku ku i Kinini "
"Akabuto in i <guilabel> ya:  </guilabel> Umwanya . "

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:36
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can now simply press the key combination you want to act as the "
"shortcut, for example <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>S</"
"keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"NONEAHA Kanda i Urufunguzo Ivanga Kuri Nka i Iy'ibusamo , ya:  Urugero: "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl; &Shift; <keycap> S </keycap> </"
"keycombo> . <guilabel> </guilabel> Ikiganiro Agasanduku Hanyuma Gufunga ku "
"Nka Nka i Iy'ibusamo ni . "

#. Tag: title
#: config.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbars"
msgstr "Imyanyabikoresho"

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:43
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sheets; has six toolbars: <guilabel>File</guilabel>, <guilabel>Edit</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Format</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Font</guilabel> and <guilabel>Color/Border</guilabel>. each of "
"which may or may not be shown depending on the choices made in the "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"&kspread; Imyanyabikoresho : Idosiye , , , , na /, Bya Gicurasi Cyangwa "
"Gicurasi OYA ku i in i <guimenu> </guimenu> Ibikubiyemo . "

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:48
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the toolbars are unlocked, you can choose whether a toolbar appears at "
"the <guimenuitem>Top</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Left</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Right</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Bottom</guimenuitem> of "
"&sheets;'s window by <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the "
"toolbar, which brings up the <guilabel>Toolbar Menu</guilabel>, and making a "
"selection from the <guisubmenu>Orientation</guisubmenu> sub menu. This "
"<guilabel>Toolbar Menu</guilabel> also has sub menus for choosing whether "
"the toolbar displays icons, text or both, and the size of the icons."
msgstr ""
"Hitamo... A Umwanyabikoresho Ku i Hejuru: , Ibumoso: , Iburyo: Cyangwa Hasi: "
"Bya &kspread; ' S Idirishya ku <mousebutton> Iburyo: </mousebutton> ku i "
"Umwanyabikoresho , Hejuru i <guilabel> </guilabel> , na A Ihitamo Kuva: i "
"<guisubmenu> </guisubmenu> Ibikubiyemo . <guilabel> </guilabel> Ibikubiyemo "
"ya:  i Umwanyabikoresho Udushushondanga , Umwandiko Cyangwa Byombi , na i "
"Ingano: Bya i Udushushondanga . "

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:56
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way of moving a toolbar is by positioning the mouse pointer over the "
"two vertical bars at the left end of each toolbar and holding the "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button down while you drag the toolbar "
"to the wanted position. When you drag the toolbar in this way you can "
"release the mouse button when it is some distance from any of &sheets;'s "
"window sides, and then you will get a floating toolbar, which is not locked "
"to any particular part of &sheets;'s window and can in fact be moved outside "
"of the window. To put a floating toolbar back into one of the traditional "
"positions <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on its titlebar to bring up "
"the <guilabel>Toolbar Menu</guilabel> then choose one of the options in the "
"<guisubmenu>Orientation</guisubmenu> sub menu."
msgstr ""
"Bya Kwimura A Umwanyabikoresho ni ku Ibirindiro i Imbeba Mweretsi KURI i "
"Kabiri Uhagaritse: Imirongo-ntambike Ku i Ibumoso: Impera Bya "
"Umwanyabikoresho na i <mousebutton> Ibumoso: </mousebutton> Imbeba Akabuto "
"Hasi Kurura i Umwanyabikoresho Kuri i Ibirindiro: . Kurura i "
"Umwanyabikoresho in iyi Irekura: i Imbeba Akabuto Ryari: ni Intera Kuva: "
"Icyo ari cyo cyose Bya &kspread; ' S Idirishya , na Hanyuma Kubona A "
"Bihindagurika Umwanyabikoresho , ni OYA ifunzwe Kuri Icyo ari cyo cyose "
"Inzira %s Bya &kspread; ' S Idirishya na in FACT Hanze Bya i Idirishya . "
"Gushyira A Bihindagurika Umwanyabikoresho Inyuma Rimwe Bya i imyanya "
"<mousebutton> Iburyo: </mousebutton> Kanda ku Kuri Hejuru i <guilabel> </"
"guilabel> Hanyuma Hitamo... Rimwe Bya i Amahitamo in i <guisubmenu> </"
"guisubmenu> Ibikubiyemo . "

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:68
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</guimenuitem> from the "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu will bring up a dialog box which lets you "
"add buttons to or remove them from &sheets;'s toolbars."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem> ... </guimenuitem> Kuva: i <guimenu> </guimenu> Ibikubiyemo "
"Hejuru A Ikiganiro Agasanduku &Ongera Utubuto Kuri Cyangwa Gukuraho Kuva: "
"&kspread; ' S Imyanyabikoresho . "

#. Tag: para
#: config.docbook:71
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use this <guilabel>Configure Toolbars</guilabel> dialog box first select "
"a toolbar from the <guilabel>Toolbar:</guilabel> combo box. The right hand "
"<guilabel>Current actions:</guilabel> window will then show the buttons "
"currently present on the toolbar. You can remove a button by selecting it in "
"this window then pressing the left arrow button, or move it around by "
"pressing the up and down arrow buttons. To add a new button to the toolbar "
"select it in the <guilabel>Available actions:</guilabel> list then press the "
"right arrow button."
msgstr ""
"Koresha iyi <guilabel> </guilabel> Ikiganiro Agasanduku Itangira Guhitamo A "
"Umwanyabikoresho Kuva: i <guilabel> : </guilabel> Agasanduku . Iburyo: "
"<guilabel> Ibikorwa : </guilabel> Idirishya Hanyuma Herekana %S i Utubuto ku "
"i Umwanyabikoresho . Gukuraho A Akabuto ku in iyi Idirishya Hanyuma i "
"Ibumoso: Akambi Akabuto , Cyangwa Himura ku i Hejuru na Hasi Akambi "
"Utubuto . &Ongera A Gishya Akabuto Kuri i Umwanyabikoresho Guhitamo in i "
"<guilabel> Ibikorwa : </guilabel> Urutonde Hanyuma Kanda i Iburyo: Akambi "
"Akabuto . "

